SynGen Inc. Key Developments

SynGen Inc. Raises $1 Million with Debt and Equity Financing in Third Financing Round of Year
Dec 2 16
SynGen Inc. has raised $1 million with debt and equity financing. The financing round is at least the third by SynGen in 2016. In July, it reported that it had raised $1 million in venture capital funding, on top of $1.6 million raised in May. The company is working to develop equipment and processes for harvesting, separating and storing bone marrow, cord blood cells and other potentially therapeutic cells for use in treating diseases.


