SynGenX Docking Station





Powerful. Efficient. Simple.



The SynGenX Docking Station transfers the data collected during the centrifuge run by the Control Module to the host PC via SynGen® DataTrak software. It also charges the Control Module’s lithium polymer ion battery. A fully charged battery will allow the Control Module to operate an average of 5 days of normal laboratory operation.


